author: IGN
description:
Check out the Warfare New Maps Trailer for Delta Force, a free-to-play action shooter developed by Team Jade. With the arrival of Season Starfall, Delta Force will come with access to two new maps with Trainwreck and Knife Edge making their way to the game. Take a look at some gameplay from the two new maps coming to Delta Force on January 18 for PC.

#DeltaForce #Gaming #IGN
title: Delta Force - Official Warfare New Maps Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Take a look at The Scissors 'Into The Future, Back to Earth' Chapter Trailer for Strinova, a free-to-play anime shooter developed by iDreamSky. 2025 has brought a new chapter and a new beginning to Strinova for both the Scissors and the Attackers. Strinova is available now for PC.

#Strinova #Gaming #IGN
title: Strinova - Official The Scissors 'Into The Future, Back to Earth' Chapter Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the Closed Beta Test Trailer for Etheria: Restart anime action turn-based strategy RPG developed by XD. Players will fight to preserve the flame of civilization as humanity transfers their consciousness into the virtual world "Etheria". Utilize combat mechanics, uncover secrets, and battle powerful foes. Etheria: Restart is available now in a Closed Beta Test for iOS, Android, and PC.

#EtheriaRestart #Gaming #IGN
title: Etheria: Restart - Official Closed Beta Test Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the Opal and Cat's Eye Story Cinematic Trailer for Wuthering Waves, an open-world action game developed by Kuro Game. Watch as Opal and Cat's Eye fall for each other in a stylish yet action-fueled manner. Wuthering Waves is available now for iOS, Android, PlayStation 5 (PS5), and PC.
